IPLookupHelper.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {
    },
	
	 lookupIP: function(ipAddress) {
        try {
            var r = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2('x_646234_ip_lookup.ipLookup', 'Default GET');
            r.setQueryParameter('ip', ipAddress);

            var response = r.executeSync(); // Synchronous execution
            var responseBody = response.getBody();
            var respObj = JSON.parse(responseBody);

            return {
                country: respObj.country_name_official || '',
                city: respObj.city || '',
                currency: respObj.currency?.name || '',
                timezone: respObj.time_zone?.name || ''
            };
        } catch (ex) {
            gs.error("IP Lookup failed: " + ex.message);
            return null;
        }
    },

    type: 'IPLookupHelper'
};]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2025-02-16 11:04:34</sys_created_on><sys_id>be53a378c3b3121093237b2ed4013101</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>IPLookupHelper</sys_name><sys_package display_value="IP lookup" source="x_646234_ip_lookup">e967d7b0c373121093237b2ed401315c</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="IP lookup">e967d7b0c373121093237b2ed401315c</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_be53a378c3b3121093237b2ed4013101</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2025-02-16 11:09:20</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
